name: Fantasy_Fields_-_Happy_Farm_Animals_Bookshelf
description:
Secure a bunch of stories with Fantasy Fields'  Happy Farm Bookcase. Friendly hand-carved farm animals line the sides of the book case, and with three levels of shelves, it is the perfect space for a growing book collection. Convenient drawer below is great for storage and collectibles.
